column2: SELECT type2_table.plate, type2_table.mjd, type2_table.fiber, type2_table.z, type2_table.survey_id, type2_table.velocity_disp, type2_table.trust_stellar_fit, type2_table.oiii_hbeta, type2_table.velocity_disp_new, type2_table.velocity_disp_new_err, photo.psfMag_u, photo.psfMag_g, photo.psfMag_r, photo.psfMag_i, photo.psfMag_z, photo.psfMagErr_u, photo.psfMagErr_g, photo.psfMagErr_r, photo.psfMagErr_i, photo.psfMagErr_z, tmass_ps.j, tmass_ps.h, tmass_ps.k, tmass_ps.jIvar, tmass_ps.hIvar, tmass_ps.kIvar, tmass.J_M_K2#FE, tmass.H_M_K2#FE, tmass.K_M_K2#FE, tmass.J_MSIG_K2#FE, tmass.H_MSIG_K2#FE, tmass.K_MSIG_K2#FE, wise.w1mpro, wise.w2mpro, wise.w3mpro, wise.w4mpro, wise.w1sigmpro, wise.w2sigmpro, wise.w3sigmpro, wise.w4sigmpro FROM MyDB.initial_type2_table as type2_table JOIN specobj as spec ON ( (spec.plate = type2_table.plate) AND (spec.mjd = type2_table.mjd) AND (spec.fiberid = type2_table.fiber) ) JOIN photoobj as photo ON (spec.specobjid = photo.specobjid) LEFT JOIN WISE_xmatch as wise_match ON (photo.objid = wise_match.sdss_objid) LEFT JOIN WISE_allsky as wise ON (wise_match.wise_cntr = wise.cntr) LEFT JOIN TwoMassXSC as tmass ON (photo.objid = tmass.objid) LEFT JOIN TwoMass as tmass_ps ON (photo.objid = tmass_ps.objid)
